data.description: BEST & FINAL DUE SUNDAY 7pm     Welcome to this beautifully up-kept bi-level home in Gloucester Twp on a quiet cul-de-sac! The home features 3 bedrooms upstairs with a jack-and-jill bathroom into the primary and an additional bedroom and bonus room on the lower level. Updated kitchen with beautiful Quartz countertops, Stainless Steel appliances, updated laminate flooring upstairs and updated vinyl flooring on lower level in the den and hallway. Newer AC & Heater (2018), Water Heater (2016). Other nice features include a Slider going out to a large deck with  above ground pool and fully fenced yard, tastefully updated walls, laundry on lower level with additional storage space, Garage with inside access. This is a truly move-in ready home offering lots of space for everyone! Close to lots of shopping, restaurants, parks and transportation. Don't delay, won't last!
